\cvsection{Work Experience}
\begin{entrylist}
    \entry{Staff Engineer - Cloud Platform}{Aug 2022 -- Present}
          {SPH Media}{Singapore}
    \begin{itemize}
        \item Led the end-to-end migration of the \href{https://www.razor.tv}{RazorTV} application from on-premises to AWS, designing the target architecture, containerizing the application with Docker, deploying it on Amazon ECS with Fargate, and leveraging AWS CloudFront for content delivery.
        \item Led the end-to-end migration of the \href{https://www.redants.sg}{RedAnts} application from on-premises to AWS, deploying the containerized application on Amazon EKS with Karpenter.
        \item Successfully completed the CDN migration for the \href{https://www.beritaharian.sg/}{BeritaHarian} website from Verizon to AWS CloudFront, developing custom logic with Lambda@Edge and CloudFront Functions to bridge feature gaps.
        \item Manage the cloud infrastructure for an application comprising 15 microservices, hosted on AWS ECS and utilizing AWS CodePipeline and GitHub Actions for CI/CD.
        \item Implemented Infrastructure as Code (IaC) using Terraform and automated CI/CD pipelines with GitHub Actions for multiple projects.
        \item Introduced and implemented AWS Verified Access to solve a key requirement for secure, VPN-less access to internal applications, and subsequently developed and published an open-source \href{https://github.com/SPHTech-Platform/terraform-aws-verified-access}{Terraform module} for the service.
        \item Built a custom extension to AWS Control Tower Account Factory for Terraform (AFT) to support modifications to existing AWS accounts, a capability not natively available, by using AWS EventBridge Pipes and AWS Lambda.
        \item Contributed a new \href{https://github.com/cloudposse/terraform-aws-waf/pull/79}{feature} to the open-source CloudPosse Terraform AWS WAF module to meet a project requirement.
        \item Contribute to the development and maintenance of internal Terraform modules.
        \item Continuous cost optimization and architectural improvements for cloud applications.
    \end{itemize}

    \newpage % Forces the following content to start on a new page

    \entry{Cloud Engineer}{Dec 2021 -- Aug 2022}
          {Bambu Robo Advisor}{Singapore}
    \begin{itemize}
        \item Managed the AWS cloud infrastructure for the Bambu Robo Advisor investment platform.
        \item Streamlined the AWS ECS infrastructure setup for over 20 microservices by leveraging AWS CDK, enabling consistent, scalable, and maintainable deployments.
        \item Automated the AWS Client-VPN setup process using AWS CDK, eliminating previous manual configurations.
        \item Reduced ECR costs by over 80\%  by implementing a targeted cross-region replication strategy and optimizing Docker images with alpine base images, which significantly decreased storage and data transfer cost.
        \item Maintained automated CI/CD workflows using AWS CodePipeline to streamline application releases.
        \item Created custom DataDog dashboards for comprehensive infrastructure monitoring.
    \end{itemize}

    \entry{Software Engineer}{Aug 2019 -- Dec 2021}
          {EROAD LTD}{New Zealand}
    \begin{itemize}
        \item Functioned in a DevOps capacity, with responsibility for both application development and AWS cloud architecture implementation.
        \item Developed Java-based microservices using the Spring Boot framework and deployed on Amazon ECS.
        \item Utilized AWS CloudFormation for Infrastructure as Code (IaC) to automate the infrastructure provisioning.
        \item Implemented and maintained CI/CD pipelines using Concourse CI to automate build and deployment workflows.
        \item Utilized AWS CloudWatch and Grafana for application monitoring and alerting.
    \end{itemize}

    \entry{Principal Software Engineer / Team Lead}{Jun 2013 -- Sep 2017}
          {SPH Media}{Singapore}
    \begin{itemize}
        \item Managed the \href{https://www.newslink.sg/}{Newslink} platform, the primary news archival system at SPH Media.
        \item Involved in both application development and infrastructure setup across On-Premises and AWS environments.
        \item Automated various infrastructure and operational tasks using AWS CloudFormation, shell scripts, and Java.
        \item Rearchitected the Newslink web application by integrating Elasticsearch, significantly improving the speed and accuracy of archival news searches.
        \item Customized the open-source Apache Nutch web crawler to fulfill specific business requirements.
        \item Led a team of three software engineers.
        \item Collaborated closely with end users and stakeholders to implement enhancements and resolve production issues promptly.
    \end{itemize}
